## 11. Hình dạng tổng thể Natt Nell

```txt
hardware substrate
  ↓
filesystem / data I-O / runtime / network
  ↓
primitive words
  ↓
Nauion Kernel
  ↓
NattCell
  ↓
EventBus / HeyNa / SmartLink
  ↓
SiraSign / Audit / Ground Truth
  ↓
ANC presence
  ↓
.kkbt render surface
```

Câu nghiệm thu tổng:

```txt
Natt Nell = hardware substrate + software fishnet + ANC presence + Nauion Kernel law + native render surface.
```

